comments: Paul (GSW) establishes himself in White's (BOS) path and does not deliver illegal contact.  The two players then move along the same path on the perimeter as they engage.
Horford (BOS) legally contests Curry's (GSW) jump shot attempt.
Kuminga (GSW) legally contests Tatum's (BOS) jump shot, making "high-five" contact after the ball is released.
Paul (GSW) reaches for the rebound and marginal contact occurs with Horford's (BOS) right arm after he tips the ball.
Jackson-Davis (GSW) reaches in as Horford (BOS) attempts to gather the rebound and makes contact with the ball.  Any ensuing contact with Horford's arms is incidental.
Horford (BOS) begins to fall to the floor on his own during the loose ball and the contact from Paul (GSW) is incidental.
The shot by Curry (GSW) is imminent within three seconds when Brown (BOS) is in the paint without actively guarding an opponent.
Horford (BOS) is the last player to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds.
Horford (BOS) briefly brings both arms around Jackson-Davis (GSW) after the screen and immediately removes them.
Brown (BOS) reaches in and makes clean contact with the ball to briefly dislodge it from Curry's (GSW) possession.
Incidental body contact occurs between White (BOS) and Curry (GSW) when the ball is loose and Curry regains possession.
Brown (BOS) legally contests Paul's (GSW) jump shot, making "high-five" contact after the ball is released.
Kuminga (GSW) legally contests Tatum's (BOS) jump shot, making "high-five" contact after the ball is released.
Jackson-Davis (GSW) possesses the rebound and Paul (GSW) signals for a timeout with 0.3 seconds remaining, but it is not recognized by officials.
Brown (BOS) moves alongside Curry's (GSW) path and maintains a legal guarding position as incidental contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
Holiday (BOS) makes clean contact with the ball reaching for the rebound and any ensuing contact with Paul (GSW) is incidental.
Holiday (BOS) is the last player to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds.
Brown (BOS) moves alongside Thompson's (GSW) path with an arm placed at his side and maintains a legal guarding position before blocking the shot attempt.
Curry (GSW) moves alongside Tatum's (BOS) path and maintains a legal guarding position before absorbing the contact initiated by Tatum during his driving shot attempt.
Horford (BOS) is the last player to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds.
Brown (BOS) jumps in the air to contest Curry's (GSW) shot attempt at the basket and the contact is marginal.
Curry (GSW) gathers the ball and legally takes two steps towards the basket as he loses his balance.
Tatum (BOS) wraps both arms around Kuminga (GSW) and dislodges him from his defensive position.
There is no clear and conclusive video evidence that confirms that Curry (GSW) makes contact with White's (BOS) arm during the jump shot attempt.
Holiday (BOS) commits a take foul on Jackson-Davis (GSW).
White (BOS) commits a take foul on Curry (GSW).
